DellAttributeRegistry.description: The DellAttributeRegistry schema contains a set of key-value pairs that represents the structure of a Registry. It includes mechanisms for building user interfaces (menus), allowing consistent navigation of the contents. The Attribute Registry is specific to a particular implementation or product. The attributes and property names are not standardized.
DellAttributeRegistry.longDescription: This resource shall be used to represent an Attribute registry for a Redfish implementation.
